title: Bobby's Virtual Surprise Birthday Party + Sam Hunt Talks New Music And The Masked Singer + Is It Okay For Eddie To Walk Outside In His Underwear?
itunes:title: Bobby's Virtual Surprise Birthday Party + Sam Hunt Talks New Music And The Masked Singer + Is It Okay For Eddie To Walk Outside In His Underwear?
description:
Bobby talks about his birthday celebrations and how everyone surprised him with a virtual surprise party. Sam Hunt joins us as the Friday Morning Conversation to talk about his new album “Southside” and his life during quarantine. Plus, Eddie walks outside in his underwear to take out the trash. He asks the show if that's okay!
